Module  : Hide Edit Notification  
Version : 1.1.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module will hide the "Edited [x] times..." notification message that
is put below a message after editing it. You can configure for which types
of users to do this (admins, moderators and/or users).

Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "hide_edit_notification" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Hide Edit Notification". 

- Go the the module's settings screen to configure for what users
  the edit message should be hidden.

